"""Final attempt: first_substantial at ANCHOR stage only.

Hypothesis: first_substantial skips shallow bumps (AF), so anchor goes deeper
(to real pia). Stage 3 band centered on real pia. Stage 3 uses normal 'first'
method so it catches fine pia edge onset (not body onset). This decouples
"where to look" (anchor) from "what to mark as pia" (Stage 3).
"""
